StackOverflow 上看见用 rich 实现终端的进度条，去 github 学习一下，在终端中提供富文本和精美格式的库，而且自带中文文档 [rich](https://github.com/Textualize/rich/blob/master/README.cn.md)  

官方提供了 [批量下载多文件的多进度条 demo](https://github.com/Textualize/rich/blob/master/examples/downloader.py) ，研究了一下比较复杂，自己写一个较为简单的批量下载示例，以 jetbrains 全家桶为例，额外增加了一个错误的下载地址

```
from pathlib import Path
from concurrent.futures import ThreadPoolExecutor
import requests
from rich.progress import Progress


def download(url, progress):
    try:
        file_name = Path(url).name

        res = requests.get(url, stream=True)
        if 200 != res.status_code:
            progress.console.log(file_name, "下载失败")
            return

        total = res.headers["Content-Length"]
        task = progress.add_task(description=file_name, total=float(total))

        with open(file_name, "wb") as f:
            for chunk in res.iter_content(chunk_size=256):
                if chunk:
                    f.write(chunk)
                    progress.update(task, advance=256)

    except Exception as msg:
        progress.console.log(file_name, "下载失败", msg)


def main():
    url_list = [
        "https://download.jetbrains.com.cn/python/error.exe",
        "https://download.jetbrains.com.cn/python/pycharm-community-2022.1.2.exe",
        "https://download.jetbrains.com.cn/idea/ideaIC-2022.1.2.exe",
        "https://download.jetbrains.com.cn/webstorm/WebStorm-2022.1.2.exe",
        "https://download.jetbrains.com.cn/python/dataspell-2022.1.2.exe",
    ]

    with Progress() as progress:
        with ThreadPoolExecutor(max_workers=2) as td_pool:
            for url in url_list:
                td_pool.submit(download, url, progress)


if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()

```
